ok...so yesterday at bowling we had our end of the year banquet where they give out all the high game, high series, 1st place team tropheys and stuff...well i got about 4 or 5 tropheys because i'm sweet like that and then the last awards where the scholarship money that we had been bowling for the last 4 weeks of the season and well i came in 1ST!!! and 1st gets a $1000!!!! The girls Danielle Fecso Won it, 2nd place which is $500 for the guys scotty don't won (scott jones) and the 2nd for the girls was my cousin!! Michelle Turnbell, ok so after the awards we got to bowl and our parents did too if the wanted too, so of course my dad did, and i kicked his ass!! But first game sucked 176, 2nd was good 235, but the last one i had the first 10 strikes and got a 289!! Today i'm going to my little sisters birthday party at my mom's house...great...But call me up because i will be really bored!!! my phone doesn't work out there so call her house 734-461-2366, ok well i wrote 2 days this weekend so no more complaining for a couple certain people, anyway got to go, peace

tonight is prom and i'm not going...this just reminds me of how lonely i really am...but anyway track is good we are 13-2 on the season and i got a new car, a 1998 caviler its really nice so thats cool umm i don't know what else to write about so i'm out peace

ITS CHRISTMAS EVE!!!!

christmas break is awesome, no school get to hang out with friends all the time and bowling whenever i want for free whats not to love?  Anyway Last weekend friday i don't think i did much break started, oh wait i lied went to the movies with jermey, Mike, maggie and cathryn to see oceans 12, it was o.k. then the twins begged for starbucks so i took them, after starbucks we all hung out at cathryns and played pool saturday i went to the mall with a bunch of people i had to pick up kris and ray ray from the D. After the mall like 15 of us went to hooters. This week monday had bowling practice shot 240 210 and like a 205. Then hung out with maples, kayla, and erica we went and saw the lights, then watched grease at kayla's house. Tuesday bowling practice again another 240 then hung out with maples and kayla again no erica this time. Wensday guess what??? bowling again and another 240 i know i'm sweet. Thursday i bowled all day, today i dont plan on doing anything so call me, if you don't know the number to bad for you
i would update but its not like anyone cares

So i figured i better update because i'm getting yelled at. Lets see not to much have been going on, bowling has been going good, we are going to win the state championship and no i'm not cocky i'm just confident. Over the weekend lets see, friday i went and watched my dad bowl. Saturday i had my bowling league in the morning then that night i went to hooter's with maples, jeff, lee, pat, scott jones, chris welsh, and danielle. Then sunday i went to this bowling fundrasier for this girl you got in to some sort of accident with a lawn mower and needs a second operation on her eye but doesn't have the money so my aunt and uncle set up this fundraiser, it was very fun it was a 9 pin no tap tourney, i couldn't bowl with the guys so i was in the kids division with my cousins that bowl for south lyon, i won plain and simple i killed them. Then on the way home from the fundraiser my dad, brother in-law, and i ended up going to hooter again.  That is about it
